subtitleNullable: tfrecords of the Kaokore japanese face dataset
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset is the Kaokore Japanese Face dataset. Currently there are 1000 of the images on this file but in the next version I will include all 8000 images. Find the original dataset here --> [KaoKore Dataset](https://github.com/rois-codh/kaokore)

- This data is for research purposes only and not for commercial use. (see github link above for more info)


### Content

All the images are 256x256 and stored in a tfrecord format. 


### Acknowledgements

Thanks to @rois-codh on github for sharing this awesome dataset!
